{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-article-index-tsx","path":"/ProgrammingDesign/zh/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>在這個科技發達的世界，許多的事情已經不需要再由我們親自處理，甚至是說句話就能完成生活的瑣事。而程式就是被設計來輔助或是自動完成我們預期的任務，小則是社交軟體；大則是人工智慧。</p>\n<h1 id=\"何為程式\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%95%E7%82%BA%E7%A8%8B%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"何為程式 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 20\" width=\"27\" height=\"27\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12.5858 4.58579C13.3668 3.80474 14.6331 3.80474 15.4142 4.58579C16.1952 5.36683 16.1952 6.63316 15.4142 7.41421L12.4142 10.4142C11.6331 11.1953 10.3668 11.1953 9.58577 10.4142C9.19524 10.0237 8.56208 10.0237 8.17156 10.4142C7.78103 10.8047 7.78103 11.4379 8.17156 11.8284C9.73365 13.3905 12.2663 13.3905 13.8284 11.8284L16.8284 8.82843C18.3905 7.26633 18.3905 4.73367 16.8284 3.17157C15.2663 1.60948 12.7337 1.60948 11.1716 3.17157L9.67156 4.67157C9.28103 5.0621 9.28103 5.69526 9.67156 6.08579C10.0621 6.47631 10.6952 6.47631 11.0858 6.08579L12.5858 4.58579ZM7.58579 9.58579C8.36683 8.80474 9.63316 8.80474 10.4142 9.58579C10.8047 9.97631 11.4379 9.97631 11.8284 9.58579C12.219 9.19526 12.219 8.5621 11.8284 8.17157C10.2663 6.60948 7.73367 6.60948 6.17157 8.17157L3.17157 11.1716C1.60948 12.7337 1.60948 15.2663 3.17157 16.8284C4.73367 18.3905 7.26633 18.3905 8.82843 16.8284L10.3284 15.3284C10.719 14.9379 10.719 14.3047 10.3284 13.9142C9.9379 13.5237 9.30474 13.5237 8.91421 13.9142L7.41421 15.4142C6.63316 16.1953 5.36684 16.1953 4.58579 15.4142C3.80474 14.6332 3.80474 13.3668 4.58579 12.5858L7.58579 9.58579Z\" fill=\"white\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"/></svg></a>何為程式</h1>\n<p>如同發明機器的原因，程式所具備最基本的能力是解決問題。\r\n它就像是黑箱一樣，每次給予同樣的輸入便會返回固定的輸出。\r\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d6154e593e305ffeaeb4d2e72fc48b4b/db540/program.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"program\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d6154e593e305ffeaeb4d2e72fc48b4b/4b190/program.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d6154e593e305ffeaeb4d2e72fc48b4b/e07e9/program.jpg 200w,\n/static/d6154e593e305ffeaeb4d2e72fc48b4b/066f9/program.jpg 400w,\n/static/d6154e593e305ffeaeb4d2e72fc48b4b/4b190/program.jpg 800w,\n/static/d6154e593e305ffeaeb4d2e72fc48b4b/e5166/program.jpg 1200w,\n/static/d6154e593e305ffeaeb4d2e72fc48b4b/b17f8/program.jpg 1600w,\n/static/d6154e593e305ffeaeb4d2e72fc48b4b/db540/program.jpg 7500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>在數學中，程式就像是函式，定義域當中的元素 x 都會對應到值域當中特定的 y。<br>\nEx.<br>\ny = f(x) = 2x + 1<br>\n=> f(1) = 3<br>\n=> f(2) = 5<br>\n=> f(3) = 7\r\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9aafe7be414a6c0d795ca2a32d9880ca/db540/function.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"function\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/9aafe7be414a6c0d795ca2a32d9880ca/4b190/function.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9aafe7be414a6c0d795ca2a32d9880ca/e07e9/function.jpg 200w,\n/static/9aafe7be414a6c0d795ca2a32d9880ca/066f9/function.jpg 400w,\n/static/9aafe7be414a6c0d795ca2a32d9880ca/4b190/function.jpg 800w,\n/static/9aafe7be414a6c0d795ca2a32d9880ca/e5166/function.jpg 1200w,\n/static/9aafe7be414a6c0d795ca2a32d9880ca/b17f8/function.jpg 1600w,\n/static/9aafe7be414a6c0d795ca2a32d9880ca/db540/function.jpg 7500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"如何學習\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%AD%B8%E7%BF%92\" aria-label=\"如何學習 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 20\" width=\"27\" height=\"27\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12.5858 4.58579C13.3668 3.80474 14.6331 3.80474 15.4142 4.58579C16.1952 5.36683 16.1952 6.63316 15.4142 7.41421L12.4142 10.4142C11.6331 11.1953 10.3668 11.1953 9.58577 10.4142C9.19524 10.0237 8.56208 10.0237 8.17156 10.4142C7.78103 10.8047 7.78103 11.4379 8.17156 11.8284C9.73365 13.3905 12.2663 13.3905 13.8284 11.8284L16.8284 8.82843C18.3905 7.26633 18.3905 4.73367 16.8284 3.17157C15.2663 1.60948 12.7337 1.60948 11.1716 3.17157L9.67156 4.67157C9.28103 5.0621 9.28103 5.69526 9.67156 6.08579C10.0621 6.47631 10.6952 6.47631 11.0858 6.08579L12.5858 4.58579ZM7.58579 9.58579C8.36683 8.80474 9.63316 8.80474 10.4142 9.58579C10.8047 9.97631 11.4379 9.97631 11.8284 9.58579C12.219 9.19526 12.219 8.5621 11.8284 8.17157C10.2663 6.60948 7.73367 6.60948 6.17157 8.17157L3.17157 11.1716C1.60948 12.7337 1.60948 15.2663 3.17157 16.8284C4.73367 18.3905 7.26633 18.3905 8.82843 16.8284L10.3284 15.3284C10.719 14.9379 10.719 14.3047 10.3284 13.9142C9.9379 13.5237 9.30474 13.5237 8.91421 13.9142L7.41421 15.4142C6.63316 16.1953 5.36684 16.1953 4.58579 15.4142C3.80474 14.6332 3.80474 13.3668 4.58579 12.5858L7.58579 9.58579Z\" fill=\"white\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"/></svg></a>如何學習</h1>\n<h2>1. 訓練邏輯思維</h2>\n<p>為了處理各種面向的問題，我們要練習解決問題的思維並將問題轉換成電腦能運算的語言 – 程式語言。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>設計出簡潔且正確的解決方式</li>\n<li>將其轉化成程式的邏輯或數學的方法，像是資料結構與演算法</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>2. 確認需求</h2>\n<p>不同的語言有著自己的獨特的特性與專長，在開發系統之前會依照使用者的需求去選擇適合的程式語言來進行開發。像是用 JavaScript 開發網頁、用 Python 訓練 AI 以及用 C++ 實作物聯網相關的嵌入式系統。</p>\n<h2>3. 學習新事物</h2>\n<p>在這個科技日新月異的時代，各項軟體更迭的速度非常地快，新穎的科技除了有更加穩定的技術之外，也包含了更加敏捷、強力的多項功能。換句話說，工程師就是站在巨人的肩膀上繼續向前走，最後便會成為下個世代的小巨人。</p>\n<h1 id=\"推薦語言\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%8E%A8%E8%96%A6%E8%AA%9E%E8%A8%80\" aria-label=\"推薦語言 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 20\" width=\"27\" height=\"27\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12.5858 4.58579C13.3668 3.80474 14.6331 3.80474 15.4142 4.58579C16.1952 5.36683 16.1952 6.63316 15.4142 7.41421L12.4142 10.4142C11.6331 11.1953 10.3668 11.1953 9.58577 10.4142C9.19524 10.0237 8.56208 10.0237 8.17156 10.4142C7.78103 10.8047 7.78103 11.4379 8.17156 11.8284C9.73365 13.3905 12.2663 13.3905 13.8284 11.8284L16.8284 8.82843C18.3905 7.26633 18.3905 4.73367 16.8284 3.17157C15.2663 1.60948 12.7337 1.60948 11.1716 3.17157L9.67156 4.67157C9.28103 5.0621 9.28103 5.69526 9.67156 6.08579C10.0621 6.47631 10.6952 6.47631 11.0858 6.08579L12.5858 4.58579ZM7.58579 9.58579C8.36683 8.80474 9.63316 8.80474 10.4142 9.58579C10.8047 9.97631 11.4379 9.97631 11.8284 9.58579C12.219 9.19526 12.219 8.5621 11.8284 8.17157C10.2663 6.60948 7.73367 6.60948 6.17157 8.17157L3.17157 11.1716C1.60948 12.7337 1.60948 15.2663 3.17157 16.8284C4.73367 18.3905 7.26633 18.3905 8.82843 16.8284L10.3284 15.3284C10.719 14.9379 10.719 14.3047 10.3284 13.9142C9.9379 13.5237 9.30474 13.5237 8.91421 13.9142L7.41421 15.4142C6.63316 16.1953 5.36684 16.1953 4.58579 15.4142C3.80474 14.6332 3.80474 13.3668 4.58579 12.5858L7.58579 9.58579Z\" fill=\"white\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"/></svg></a>推薦語言</h1>\n<h2>1. <a href=\"https://www.python.org/\">Python</a></h2>\n<p>Python 是目前最受歡迎的程式語言，因為包含了新穎的語法風格、眾多的第三方套件與活絡的大型社群，因此許多新手選擇它當作啟蒙的程式語言。</p>\n<h2>2. <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-TW/docs/Learn/JavaScript/First_steps/What_is_JavaScript\">JavaScript</a></h2>\n<p>由於我的專業項目是網頁開發，因此推薦的另一個語言是 JavaScript。它擁有與 Python 相似、極為自由的語法，且包含了跨平台執行環境 <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/zh-tw\">Node.js</a>（開放原始碼），讓它不再受限於網頁前端，能夠在伺服器端運行端運行。</p>\n<p>會推薦這兩個程式語言是因為它們都易於安裝與配置環境，甚至是打開瀏覽器就可以直接執行，而且它們相較於其他的程式語言有著更高階的邏輯與更為自由的語法。\r\n讓我們開始學習之旅吧！</p>","fields":{"date":"2023/ 04/ 17"},"frontmatter":{"title":"程式設計"}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"nodes":[{"frontmatter":{"title":"程式設計"},"fields":{"depth":0,"path":"/ProgrammingDesign/zh"}}]}},"pageContext":{"id":"21f25e7b-ea15-58b8-8d34-a8cf1451b38b","regexContents":"/^ProgrammingDesign$|^ProgrammingDesign//","language":"zh"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2455516822","2714612279","3936017631"],"slicesMap":{}}